---
interface Props {
  included: string[];
  excluded: string[];
  extras: string[];
}

const { included, excluded, extras } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="inex section-pad">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label inex-reveal">El alcance</p>
    <h2 class="inex-h2 inex-reveal">Qué incluye<br />y qué no.</h2>
    <p class="inex-intro inex-reveal">
      El foco estrecho no es una limitación. Es lo que permite cumplir la promesa y mantener el margen bajo control.
    </p>

    <div class="inex-grid">
      <div class="inex-col inex-reveal">
        <p class="inex-col-label inex-col-label--in">Incluido en el fee mensual</p>
        <ul class="inex-list" role="list">
          {included.map((item) => (
            <li class="inex-item inex-item--in">
              <span class="inex-check" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path d="M2.5 7L5.5 10L11.5 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="inex-col inex-reveal inex-reveal-delay-1">
        <p class="inex-col-label inex-col-label--out">No incluido</p>
        <ul class="inex-list" role="list">
          {excluded.map((item) => (
            <li class="inex-item inex-item--out">
              <span class="inex-dash" aria-hidden="true">—</span>
              {item}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="inex-extras inex-reveal">
      <p class="inex-extras-label">Fuera del alcance estándar · se cotiza aparte</p>
      <div class="inex-extras-chips">
        {extras.map((item) => (
          <span class="extras-chip">{item}</span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="inex-note inex-reveal">
      La pauta publicitaria siempre va aparte. El cliente la paga directamente a Google. Nunca la incluimos en el fee — así mantenemos las cuentas en manos del cliente y sin opacidad.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .inex {
    background: var(--color-sage);
  }

  .inex-h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-h2-size);
    font-weight: var(--text-h2-weight);
    letter-spacing: var(--text-h2-track);
    line-height: var(--text-h2-leading);
    color: var(--color-forest);
    margin-block: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .inex-intro {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-lede-size);
    line-height: var(--text-lede-leading);
    color: var(--color-olive);
    max-width: 52ch;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .inex-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .inex-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
    }
  }

  .inex-col-label {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .inex-col-label--in {
    color: var(--color-orange);
  }
  .inex-col-label--out {
    color: var(--color-olive);
  }

  .inex-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .inex-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-body-size);
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding-block: 0.875rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-moss);
  }
  .inex-item:first-child {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-moss);
  }

  .inex-item--in {
    color: var(--color-forest);
  }
  .inex-item--out {
    color: var(--color-olive);
  }

  .inex-check {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--color-orange);
    margin-top: 0.1em;
    display: flex;
  }

  .inex-dash {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--color-moss);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .inex-extras {
    background: var(--color-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-moss);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .inex-extras-label {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-olive);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .inex-extras-chips {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .extras-chip {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-forest);
    background: var(--color-sage);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-moss);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 0.375rem 0.875rem;
  }

  .inex-note {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-body-size);
    line-height: var(--text-body-leading);
    color: var(--color-olive);
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }
</style>
